The '''Suporro Sea''' was a sea on [[Brentaal IV/Legends|Brentaal IV]]. The [[Gravaal mountain range|Gravaal Mountains]] passed close to it near the city of [[Cormond]], which lay along its coast.<ref name="CCW">''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]''</ref>

